Nicki Rapp https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nicki_Rapp 0 Nicki Rapp (often credited as Nikki Rapp)(born 4 September 1972 in Santa Rosa, California, USA) is an American video game voice actress known for providing the voices for Lili Zanotto in Psychonauts, Morgan LeFlay in Tales of Monkey Island, Lilly in The Walking Dead video game, and the children in several games in The Sims franchise.
